snippet.title: Crowdfunding Trailer - Path of Titans
snippet.description:
INDIEGOGO IS LIVE! https://igg.me/at/pathoftitans

Path of Titans is a multiplayer dinosaur survival video game being developed for home computers and mobile devices. Survive as a dinosaur in a rich ecosystem filled with intelligent AI creatures and up to 200 other players. Explore a realistic, detailed environment and complete objectives with herd and pack members alike.

Frequent updates by the developers will add new content, and we will also provide the community with powerful modding tools to create their own dream projects.

For more information please check out https://pathoftitans.com
#pathoftitans #dinosaurvideogame #survivalgame
